# Default flags for `act` (https://github.com/nektos/act), which runs
# .github/workflows/*.yml locally in Docker. Use as the escape hatch when
# `make ci` passes locally but GitHub Actions fails — most often a
# services/container or runner-environment difference.
#
# The medium image carries Go, Node, jq, etc. — closer parity with
# ubuntu-latest than the default micro image, at a ~1.5GB download cost.
-P ubuntu-latest=catthehacker/ubuntu:act-latest
--container-architecture linux/amd64
